ali anche a chi è rimasto a casa.</p><p>Altra filiale:</p><p>Yalda Sihlcity<br />Kalanderplatz 1<br />8045 Zürich</p>','Yalda Europaallee','Yalda Europaallee','Yalda Europaallee','Yalda Europaallee','Die beliebtesten Rezepte der orientalischen Küche, modern interpretiert und vor Ort frisch zubereitet.','The best recipes from Middle Eastern cuisine, freshly prepared and interpreted in a modern way.','Les plats orientaux les plus populaires, interprétés de façon moderne et préparés sur place.','Le ricette più amate della cucina orientale interpretate in chiave moderna e preparate fresche.','https://cdn.zuerich.com/sites/default/files/web_zuerich_restaurant_yalda_1280x960_24358.jpg','https://cdn.zuerich.com/sites/default/files/web_zuerich_restaurant_yalda_1280x960_24357.jpg','2019-10-03 17:52:33 +0200','In der Europaallee','Located at the Europaallee','Tout près de la gare centrale','Presso l’Europaallee','CH','Zürich',8004,'Gustav-Gull-Platz 2','europaallee@yalda.ch','www.yalda.ch',47.379256717915,8.530952578476,'<p>Montag bis Donnerstag, 10.00 &ndash; 23.00 Uhr<br />Freitag, 10.00 &ndash; 24.00 Uhr<br />Samstag, 11.00 &ndash; 24.00 Uhr</p>','<p>Monday &ndash; Thursday, 10am &ndash; 11pm<br />Friday, 10am &ndash; 12pm<br />Saturday, 11am &ndash; 12pm</p>','<p>Du lundi au jeudi, 10h &ndash; 23h<br />Vendredi, 10h &ndash; 24h<br />Samedi, 11h &ndash; 24h</p>','<p>Da lunedì a giovedì, 10.00 &ndash; 23.00<br />Venerdì, 10.00 &ndash; 24.00<br />Sabato, 11.00 &ndash; 24.00</p>','Monday,Tuesday,Wednesday,Thursday,Friday,Saturday','POINT (47.379256717915 8.530952578476001)',4,NULL,'+41 44 542 88 99',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),
