cks.','The feel-good oasis with living room charm offers delicious cakes, coffee and snacks.','Délicieux gâteaux, café et en-cas sont servis dans le charmant salon de cette oasis de bien-être.','Un’oasi di benessere col fascino di un salotto, che serve torte, caffè e snack.','https://cdn.zuerich.com/sites/default/files/web_zuerich_platzhalterbild_4833_0.jpg',NULL,'2018-09-05 11:21:14 +0200','Leckere Kuchen, Kaffee und Lunchs','Delicious cakes, coffee and lunches','Délicieux gâteaux, café et lunchs','Caffè e ristorante',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),
